    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> to a heatproof bowl, cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until the potato is fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
