      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the paneer and cashews are starting to brown, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
