    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>paneer,</strong> <strong>sweet potato & cashew curry</strong> over the <strong>cooked brown rice</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly over the curry with<strong> </strong>scissors</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
